==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Abysmal
<hw>A*bys"mal</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to, or
resembling, an abyss; bottomless; unending; profound.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Geology gives one the same <qex>abysmal</qex> extent of time that
astronomy does of space.</q> <rj><qau>Carlyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Abysmally</ent>⟦br⟧
